{"tid":2493292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵員工跪頸打人企圖謀殺係半年前已可預見的","createTime":"2021-04-17T19:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T21:36:14.000Z","uid":26770,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f4d1f48cec6c54d2acb35941b26e5248dbc4c2","tid":2493292,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T19:10:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210418/STZJQR2HI5GVZKU3JRZCNI7KSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210418%2FSTZJQR2HI5GVZKU3JRZCNI7KSM%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=46215961\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210418%2FSTZJQR2HI5GVZKU3JRZCNI7KSM%2F&h=91efb6e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210418/STZJQR2HI5GVZKU3JRZCNI7KSM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>遭警圍扑頭破血流 棄考 DSE 離港休養 大埔少年人生怎樣被警暴改寫？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%80%E5%B4%8E%E5%B6%87%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%AD-1-%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%9C%8D%E6%89%91%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81-%E6%A3%84%E8%80%83-dse-%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%91%E9%A4%8A-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%80%8E%E6%A8%A3%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4%E6%94%B9%E5%AF%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B4%258E%25E5%25B6%2587%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25AD-1-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%2589%2591%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%25B5%2581-%25E6%25A3%2584%25E8%2580%2583-dse-%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BC%2591%25E9%25A4%258A-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2580%258E%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%25AF%25AB%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=aaa2a226\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B4%258E%25E5%25B6%2587%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25AD-1-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%2589%2591%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%25B5%2581-%25E6%25A3%2584%25E8%2580%2583-dse-%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BC%2591%25E9%25A4%258A-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2580%258E%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%25AF%25AB%2F&h=6b0de6af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%80%E5%B4%8E%E5%B6%87%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%AD-1-%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%9C%8D%E6%89%91%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81-%E6%A3%84%E8%80%83-dse-%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%91%E9%A4%8A-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%80%8E%E6%A8%A3%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4%E6%94%B9%E5%AF%AB/</a><br />\n<br />\n跪頸,打頭其實有好高致命風險,當然在李家超及林鄭縱容下無從追究<br />\n一堆離奇自殺案真相是很明顯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2179229/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2179229/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n半年前有後生仔行過黨鐵遭香港警魔亂棍打頭, 情緒病嚴重到考唔到DSE<br />\n當時就有畜牲小黃人立即封出口阻擋記者<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">黨鐵內有技能專業資格的人都尚正常<br />\n班私人市場撈唔起的袋底泥著條制服當自己差佬, 打客唔係第一次<span class=\"xx-large\">, 因為黨鐵請大量退休差佬高層,到最後打人者反而在差佬掩護下變報稱受傷的'受害人'</span></span><br />\n<ins>但班袋底泥出去私人市場撈唔起, 著起制服就FF自己係差佬<br />\n查飛查到打人已經唔係第一次, 係死差佬偏袒下從來只誣告受害人</ins>"},{"pid":"b1a75daa5a4eda7d28d8bdd7540b542bfc47ec68","tid":2493292,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T19:16:12.000Z","msg":"當&lt;竟&gt;權變左變政權維穩機器........人民仲可以點做....??<br />\n<br />\n好似緬甸咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44674c9bc76283ad17a2430f02558ff497a7a007","tid":2493292,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T19:19:21.000Z","msg":"大財團請大量退休狗隊中層至高層以便其手下犯法時獲得庇佑<br />\n<br />\n香港貪污情況一直係好嚴重<br />\n只係傳媒唔報,用延後利益/惠及家人等間接方法放水<br />\n<br />\nICAC一直都係捉超市經理炒奶粉, 電器鋪經理仔後門貨炒IPHONE谷高定罪人數,ICAC 放生罪犯唔係721單野先開始<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">只係香港人睇完咩Q野<ins>廉政行動20XX</ins> 就覺得自己好了解班撚人<br />\n實際上呢類電視.電影係大內孫<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"cc7120c98bfab6240b72ca611e523ed3d9a0fbb3","tid":2493292,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T19:25:13.000Z","msg":"班查飛狗根本係顛狗<br />\n壓頸係可以終生傷殘<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下幾惡毒的人先做得出<br />\n又唔係捉銀行劫匪/恐怖份子<br />\n<span class=\"red\">只係走張車飛錢就想整到人殘廢WOR</span>"},{"pid":"40820214d9895ce3fbfda553839fe281eb517614","tid":2493292,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T19:33:00.000Z","msg":"其實已經仲恐怖過支那<br />\n上海果類大城市要做門面, 攪大左經常割席交人<br />\n因為太柒黨媒同小粉紅係唔會唱開<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"blue\"><ins>現在香港就係坐黨鐵都隨時無故比人打死,恐怖過當時泰國政變</ins></span><br />\n泰國政變因各方勢力知旅客係搖錢樹所以唔會去攻擊</ins><br />\n<br />\n香港已經係中東級數,你搭黨鐵根本就唔會有信心見到下一日的太陽"},{"pid":"828576c8bd296b8de313c34b5523a45249f81e4b","tid":2493292,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T19:45:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d9823618459ad26402e27d0a51dd070d9e38d4b","tid":2493292,"uid":202921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc7120c98bfab6240b72ca611e523ed3d9a0fbb3","tid":2493292,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T19:25:13.000Z","msg":"班查飛狗根本係顛狗<br />\n壓頸係可以終生傷殘<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下幾惡毒的人先做得出<br />\n又唔係捉銀行劫匪/恐怖份子<br />\n<span class=\"red\">只係走張車飛錢就想整到人殘廢WOR</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T20:06:03.000Z","msg":"佢仲要唔係搭霸王車 <br />\n而係用返佢有權用嘅殘疾人士八達通搭車 <br />\n然後比隻查飛狗屈鳩佢 但人地明明就有公立醫院出嘅證明<br />\n<br />\n根本呢單野唔係癲咗咁簡單 <br />\n而係切切實實嘅hate crime <br />\n告鳩柒佢老母閪啦 仆街查飛狗"},{"pid":"113512fc531f01b72cb4b8a4c7819d72a9b23d30","tid":2493292,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d9823618459ad26402e27d0a51dd070d9e38d4b","tid":2493292,"uid":202921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc7120c98b